# OIS Integration Intelligence: Notion × Fourthwall × YouTube × Discord × OBS

> **Version:** 1.1 — March 4, 2026
> **Status:** Living document. Built with verified primary and secondary sources.
> **Intended use:** AI project context, agent instructions, architecture reference, developer onboarding.
> **Source of truth hierarchy:** Fourthwall owns transactions. Discord owns community presence. OBS owns stream state. YouTube owns content performance. Notion is the ledger — it receives signals from all of them.

