## 6. Fourthwall-Specific: The API Most Creators Don't Know Exists

The Open API is not invite-only. Any SUPER ADMIN can generate credentials under Settings → For Developers. Full documentation: `docs.fourthwall.com`.

**Three-API architecture:**
- **Platform API** — backend operations (orders, products, fulfillment, webhooks). Basic Auth.
- **Storefront API** — public-facing product data. Read-only. `ptkn_*` storefront token.
- **Memberships API** — membership posts and content.

The Platform API's webhook CRUD endpoints let you manage subscriptions programmatically — an n8n workflow can self-register its callback URL.

**Zapier is the privileged middleware partner.** Native Zapier integration with 12 instant triggers and 4 actions. No other major middleware (Make.com, n8n, Pipedream) has a native Fourthwall module — all require generic webhook triggers. Pre-built Zapier templates exist for Fourthwall → Discord orders and Fourthwall → Discord subscriptions.

**Notable ecosystem integrations:** Twitch gifting and Sub Discounts for memberships (up to 80% off), StreamElements merch rotator widget, BookFunnel integration for automated ebook delivery, Streamer.bot direct integration. GitHub org `FourthwallHQ` hosts a Vercel Commerce headless storefront template and example repos.

