## 8. Integration Middleware: Choosing the Right Tool Per Chain

### Free tier comparison

| Platform | Free allowance | Multi-step workflows | Polling interval | Native Fourthwall |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Make.com** | 1,000 credits/mo | 2 scenarios | 15 min | ❌ |
| **Zapier** | 100 tasks/mo | 2-step only | 15 min | ✅ |
| **n8n self-hosted** | Unlimited | Unlimited | Any | ❌ |
| **Pipedream** | 100 credits/mo | 3 workflows | — | ❌ |

### Recommended stack for Outside Inn Studios

At ~50-200 orders/month and a few streams per week, estimated total automation events are 200-920/month — fits comfortably within Make.com Core ($9/month) or Zapier Professional ($19.99/month), and is essentially free on n8n self-hosted.

| Chain | Recommended tool | Cost | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| Fourthwall → Discord membership roles | **Fourthwall native** | $0 | Handles Scrivener/Keeper → Discord role mapping |
| Fourthwall → Discord order/donation notifications | **fw-webhooks.vercel.app** | $0 | Or Zapier template for richer formatting |
| Fourthwall → Notion order/membership logging | **Zapier** or **n8n** | $0-$19.99/mo | Zapier for native trigger; n8n for lowest cost |
| OBS → Discord stream alerts | **StreamNotifier** | $0 | Direct, no cloud dependency |
| OBS → Notion stream logging | **Advanced Scene Switcher + n8n** | ~$5/mo | curl macro → n8n webhook → Notion API |
| YouTube → Discord live/upload alerts | **NotifyMe or Pingcord** | $0 | Handles PubSubHubbub internally |
| YouTube → Notion stream logging | **n8n** | ~$5/mo | PubSubHubbub callback → videos.list → Notion |
| Notion → Discord announcements | **Notion automation + n8n** | ~$5/mo | Notion "Send webhook" → n8n → Discord webhook |

**Budget-optimized path:** n8n self-hosted on a $5/month VPS handles all middleware chains except the zero-code natives. Total: **~$5/month** for unlimited automation with full code control.

**Lowest-effort path:** Zapier Professional ($19.99/month) for all Fourthwall chains (native triggers), supplemented by StreamNotifier and NotifyMe for zero-code legs. No server management, no bridge scripts beyond StreamNotifier.

