## 9. Integration Roadmap

### Phase 1 — Zero cost, deploy this week

These require no middleware spend and can be deployed today.

- [ ] Fourthwall native Discord integration → Scrivener and Keeper role assignment
- [ ] StreamNotifier OBS plugin → Discord go-live alerts
- [ ] NotifyMe or Pingcord → YouTube upload/live → Discord notifications

### Phase 2 — Notion as system of record (first month)

- [ ] Fourthwall webhooks → Notion Members CRM (new Scrivener/Keeper rows)
- [ ] Fourthwall webhooks → Notion Orders log (all purchases)
- [ ] OBS StreamStateChanged → Notion Word Counter On-Stream entries
- [ ] Notion Calendar [Core] milestone marked Done → Discord announcement

### Phase 3 — Automation + intelligence (April/May)

- [ ] YouTube Analytics weekly pull → Notion stream performance dashboard
- [ ] Notion Custom Agent → stream recap generation from Stream Log database
- [ ] OBS celebrations: Fourthwall membership → Streamer.bot → OBS scene switch
- [ ] PubSubHubbub subscription → live stream detection with liveBroadcasts.list fallback poll

### Unsolved / requires custom build

- Identity linking for non-membership purchases: Discord `/verify` bot command backed by Fourthwall API lookup
- Automatic patron roll updates: obs-websocket-js `SetInputSettings` call on new Scrivener/Keeper join

